cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.NE 

The paper discusses the use of deep learning for medical image reconstruction, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of parallel-, fan- and cone-beam projectors and back-projectors, which are related to information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the paper discusses the use of a high-level Python API for conducting experiments, which is related to neural networks (cs.NE).
